    public class MaterialCheckBox
extends BaseCheckBox
implements HasGrid
    Checkbox component provides two types - FILLED - INTERMEDIATE

    UiBinder Usage:

     
 // Default
 <m:MaterialCheckBox text="Option 1"/>

 // Filled
 <m:MaterialCheckBox text="Option 1" type="FILLED"/>

    Author:
    kevzlou7979, Ben Dol
    See Also:
    CheckBox, Material Design Specification
